{
  "name": "baymax",
  "version": "0.0.1",
  "description": "Sistema de Integracao ERP DoutorJA",
  "main": "server.js",
  "author": "doutorja",
  "license": "MIT",
  "private": true,
  "engines": {
    "node": ">= 8.11.0"
  },
  "scripts": {
    "starts": "nodemon ./app/server.js -e js,json --exec babel-node",
    "startwindows": "babel-node --inspect=5858 ./app/server.js",
    "start": "pm2 start ./dist/server.js",
    "ts": "nodemon ./server.js -e js,json --exec babel-node",
    "prebuild": "rm -rf ./dist",
    "build": "./node_modules/.bin/babel ./app --out-dir dist/",
    "debug": "babel-node ./app/server.js --nolazy --inspect=9229",
    "test": "NODE_ENV=test mocha test --exit",
    "generatedoc": "./node_modules/.bin/esdoc"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "babel-cli": "6.26.0",
    "babel-eslint": "8.2.6",
    "babel-plugin-transform-async-generator-functions": "^6.24.1",
    "babel-plugin-transform-object-rest-spread": "6.26.0",
    "babel-plugin-transform-runtime": "^6.23.0",
    "babel-preset-env": "1.7.0",
    "babel-preset-es2015": "^6.24.1",
    "babel-preset-minify": "0.4.3",
    "esdoc": "^1.1.0",
    "esdoc-brand-plugin": "^1.0.1",
    "esdoc-standard-plugin": "^1.0.0",
    "eslint": "^5.4.0",
    "eslint-config-airbnb": "17.1.0",
    "eslint-config-prettier": "^3.0.1",
    "eslint-plugin-import": "2.14.0",
    "eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y": "6.1.1",
    "eslint-plugin-node": "^7.0.1",
    "eslint-plugin-prettier": "^2.6.2",
    "eslint-plugin-react": "7.11.0",
    "nodemon": "^1.18.3",
    "prettier": "1.14.0",
    "prettier-standard": "^8.0.1",
    "prettierrc": "0.0.0-5"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "body-parser": "^1.18.3",
    "express": "^4.16.3",
    "express-winston": "^3.0.0",
    "filter-files": "^0.4.0",
    "is-directory": "^0.3.1",
    "lodash": "^4.17.10",
    "morgan": "^1.9.0",
    "node-fetch": "^2.2.0",
    "node-json-transform": "^1.0.17",
    "unirest": "^0.5.1",
    "winston": "^3.0.0"
  }
}
